Can't nobody tell me
global warming ain't real, man,

14:22.762 --> 14:25.596
all that craziness out there.

14:25.631 --> 14:27.431
It wasn't like this
when we was kids, you know.

14:27.466 --> 14:30.368
I hope that my gloves
didn't get wet.

14:30.403 --> 14:33.371
All that stuff
for that motorcycle of yours?

14:33.406 --> 14:35.039
Mm-hmm. You know
I wanted to ride today

14:35.074 --> 14:36.974
They got all wet.

14:37.009 --> 14:38.876
Now, I got you
a helmet in here.

14:38.911 --> 14:40.611
I hope you saved
your receipt.

14:40.646 --> 14:44.115
