on that road before long,

14:44.150 --> 14:47.551
have your arms
wrapped around me,

14:47.586 --> 14:48.753
wind blowing
in your face.

14:48.788 --> 14:50.021
Don't that sound nice?

14:50.056 --> 14:51.789
That's a bet you gonna lose,

14:51.824 --> 14:53.824
'cause, like I told you,
I ain't getting on that thing.

14:53.859 --> 14:56.360
Baby, you ain't no fun.

14:56.395 --> 14:58.663
