<i> ¶ Blow it out the window ¶</i>

15:52.151 --> 15:55.119
<i> ¶ Mm mm ¶</i>

15:56.022 --> 15:58.022
Are you okay?

15:59.091 --> 16:00.725
You've been
a little quiet.

16:02.028 --> 16:03.361
I'm okay.

16:04.330 --> 16:06.364
Just got a lot
on my mind.

16:07.633 --> 16:09.467
I'm not mad or nothing.

16:14.106 --> 16:15.540
You want to dance?

16:17.043 --> 16:18.342
What?

16:18.377 --> 16:21.078
I mean, since
it's looking doubtful

16:21.113 --> 16:24.281
we'll get out of here safely,

16:24.316 --> 16:27.418
I figured I could show you
some of my moves.

16:35.728 --> 16:37.462
[slow dance music plays]

16:41.734 --> 16:45.136
<i> ¶ Ohh ¶</i>

16:45.171 --> 16:48.672
<i> ¶ Hey ¶</i>

16:48.707 --> 16:50.007
Wow.

16:50.042 --> 16:51.709
<i> ¶ You don't know, babe ¶</i>

16:51.744 --> 16:53.044
[laughs]

16:53.079 --> 16:55.813
<i> ¶ When you hold me ¶</i>

16:55.848 --> 16:57.648
<i> ¶ You kiss me slowly ¶</i>

16:57.683 --> 17:01.385
<i> ¶ It's the sweetest thing... ¶</i>

17:01.420 --> 17:03.687
I'm sorry I didn't tell you
about the other room.

17:03.722 --> 17:08.759
I just kept it as a surprise.

17:08.794 --> 17:10.561
I know we made plans,
but...

17:12.131 --> 17:14.065
I didn't want
to assume anything.

17:15.134 --> 17:16.901
I didn't want you
to feel pressure.

17:16.936 --> 17:18.536
You know?

17:18.571 --> 17:20.905
I didn't want to be unprepared,
though, so I just got it--

17:20.940 --> 17:22.740
It's okay, Micah.

17:26.745 --> 17:29.313
I didn't want
to be unprepared, either.

17:29.348 --> 17:32.850
So that's why I went
on birth control pills

17:32.885 --> 17:34.585
six weeks ago.

17:36.856 --> 17:38.222
Okay.

17:40.459 --> 17:41.459
[sighs]

17:41.494 --> 17:44.328
So we should get
the other room, or...

17:45.297 --> 17:47.498
I don't--I don't know.

17:47.533 --> 17:50.835
It doesn't feel like
what I thought it would be.

17:52.338 --> 17:54.305
Yeah, I feel that way, too.

17:54.340 --> 18:00.911
<i> ¶ Ohh</i>
<i> You're the best part... ¶</i>

18:00.946 --> 18:04.449
How do you know
when it's right?

18:05.417 --> 18:06.717
<i> ¶ If you love me ¶</i>

18:06.752 --> 18:08.752
<i> ¶ Won't you say something? ¶</i>

18:08.787 --> 18:10.821
<i> ¶ If you love me, won't you ¶</i>

